The paper proposes a method for regularizing trajectory optimization using a denoising autoencoder. This involves learning dynamics models and using them to optimize trajectories. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), systems and control (cs.SY), and computer vision (cs.CV).
